  <h2>Our principles</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Prevention over reaction.</strong> Smart defaults, smart limits, smart matching.</li>
    <li><strong>Humans in the loop.</strong> Every report goes to a real person, fast.</li>
    <li><strong>Transparency.</strong> Clear rules, clear consequences, no shadow bans.</li>
    <li><strong>User control.</strong> You decide who sees you, what you share, and when.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How we do it</h2>
  <p>We combine machine learning for pattern detection with a 24/7 human review team trained in trauma-informed care. We partner with leading non-profits and report transparently every quarter.</p>

